<option value="char5">Imezzed - 6th Enchanter</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub30.ezboard.com/utaladan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Taladan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sentinent Member</span><br>  Posts: 178<br> <font color=#333333>(3/5/01 6:16:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Good thought ...</span><hr size=1> Personally I have yet to fight in Velious and have little knowledge of the intricacies faction will play, other than what has been listed in this thread.<br>
<br>
Will be a tough one to deal with as a group as it appears some have already started along thier own path in this area. I do agree it is something some of us may desire to make a &quot;joint&quot; effort on and am wondering how we could &quot;dicuss&quot; it more easily.<br>
<br>
One idea, least for fact finding, would be to compile some stats on who is already where in the faction tables. Glad to come up with something for now and in the future.  Perhaps if those with set faction wanted to email me I could do a post listing same.<br>
<br>
I would think a bit more discussion would be required in order for others, including myself, to determine which direction they would want to take on this. Personally I would prefer to make a decision, along with others, to help make grouping in the future easier. I would not expect the entire guild to go anyone direction but it will be helpful to know who else we/I have in the same faction set we/I am.<br>
<br>
T'Dan<br>
